name: Sweet memory #1
description:
In a story of life, of course there are many things that we can learn, one of which is from the past. The past gives us the opportunity to change ourselves for a better life. 
In this case, through the LP's that is played, it flows beautifully along with the love stories that grow between us. Of course all of that can provide sweet memories for yourself and even a story that can be shared with everyone. Very beautiful isn't it?
